 -----Original Message-----
From: 	"Onukogu, Ernest" <Ernest.Onukogu@dowjones.com>@ENRON [mailto:IMCEANOTES-+22Onukogu+2C+20Ernest+22+20+3CErnest+2EOnukogu+40dowjones+2Ecom+3E+40ENRON@ENRON.com] 
